United Colors of Benetton Flip Flops Price: Rs.999

Splashed with a rich hue of red and white all over
column17:
this pair of bright flip flops from United Colors of Benetton lends a fun flair to your weekend look. The padded footbed and textured outsole ensure incredible comfort and support. You can team these flip flops with a printed top and denim shorts.\xa0

United Colors of Benetton gives the rebellious youth footwear that is renowned for its fine Italian designs and peppy colours to celebrate their individuality.

Footwear Care

Treat these flip flops with utmost care by wiping them with a damp cloth.
